## Tooling

### Makefile commands

```makefile
.PHONY: build test lint fmt vet

build:
	go build -o bin/app ./cmd/myapp

test:
	go test ./... -race -count=1

test-short:
	go test ./... -short

lint:
	golangci-lint run ./...

fmt:
	gofmt -w .
	goimports -w .

vet:
	go vet ./...

tidy:
	go mod tidy
```

